product.name: ACLONG Tape-On Rain Guards Fit for Toyota RAV4 2019 2020 2021 2022 2023 Tape-On Smoke Side Shatterproof Window Visor, Out-Channel Window Deflectors, 6-Pieces Set
product.description: Super easy to install, literally took about 10-15 minutes.
product.bullet_points:
• 【Rain guards fit for Toyota RAV4】: Compatible with Toyota RAV4 2019 2020 2021 2022 2023, were designed to resemble an OE appearance
• 【SMOKE COLOR】: RAV4 Window Visor choose the finest Material for sun protection, Enhance the Look of your car and make it more comfortable to drive.Note: Due to the material of the rain guards, its curvature will change a little bit when it was squeezed during transportation,please gently bend it according to the car's window when installing
• 【Let Fresh air to Enter, Reducing Wind Noise】：ACLONG rain guards fit for Toyota RAV4 have 3D aerodynamically designed to reduce wind noise while channeling airflow to keep your vehicles interior free of smoke, stale air and window fogging, rain around your window while still allowing air to flow
• 【Easy to Install】: NO special hardware, NO drilling necessary, Just in 10-15 Minutes window visors can be installed. Rain visor Includes adhesive tape, very stable and won't fall off on the highway
• 【Flexible & Shatterproof】: ACLONG side window deflectors made of high quality reinforced acrylic with light weight design UV-Resistant,flexible, shatterproof, will not break
